column6: This amendment discloses an additional contribution to Thom Tillis Committee (FEC ID C00545772). Check 31625 for $2450.00 was originally issued to this committee on 6/27/19 and reported on the 2019 July Monthly Report. In December, we were notified that the check was never received, and a replacement check was issued. Check 31625 was reported on the 2019 January 31 Year-End Report as a prior period void. In reviewing the January bank statement, we found that both the original and replacement checks had been presented for payment. We have requested a refund of $2450.00 from the committee; such refund will be disclosed on the March monthly report.
